<reference id="api_iaudioframeobserverbase_getrecordaudioparams_iaudioframeobserverbase">
    <title><ph keyref="getRecordAudioParams_IAudioFrameObserverBase"/></title>
    <shortdesc id="short"><ph id="shortdesc" props="cpp"><xref keyref="onRecordAudioFrame_IAudioFrameObserverBase"/> 回调的音频格式设置回调。</ph></shortdesc>
    <prolog>
        <metadata>
            <keywords>
                <indexterm keyref="getRecordAudioParams_IAudioFrameObserverBase"/>
            </keywords>
        </metadata>
    </prolog>
    <refbody>
        <section id="prototype">
            <p outputclass="codeblock">
                <codeblock props="cpp" outputclass="language-cpp">virtual AudioParams getRecordAudioParams() = 0;</codeblock>
            </p>
        </section>
        <section id="detailed_desc" deliveryTarget="details" otherprops="no-title">
            <p props="cpp">调用 <xref keyref="registerAudioFrameObserver_IMediaEngine"/> 注册音频帧观察者后，SDK 会触发该回调。你可以在该回调的返回值中设置音频格式。</p>
            <note props="cpp">SDK 会根据你在返回值中设置的 <xref keyref="AudioParams"/> 计算采样间隔，并以此触发 <xref keyref="onRecordAudioFrame_IAudioFrameObserverBase"/> 回调。采样间隔的计算公式为：采样间隔（秒） = <codeph>samplePerCall</codeph> /（<codeph>sampleRate</codeph> × <codeph>channel</codeph>）。请确保采样间隔 ≥ 0.01 秒。</note>
        </section>
        <section id="timing" deliveryTarget="details" props="cpp">
            <title>调用时机</title>
            <p props="cpp">加入频道前后均可调用。</p>
        </section>
        <section id="return_values" props="cpp">
            <title>返回值</title>
            <p props="cpp">方法调用成功时，返回一个 <xref keyref="AudioParams"/> 实例，详见 <xref keyref="AudioParams"/>。</p>
        </section>
    </refbody>
</reference>